The paper deals with interpreting predictive models hidden behind APIs, which is a common problem in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper proposes a closed form solution for interpreting Piecewise Linear Models (PLM), which is a popular classification model. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
